## A small module that:

1.Increments the address (usually PC + 4 for 32-bit instructions)
2.Allows branching/jumping

CODE:
module program_counter (
    input logic clk,
    input logic reset,
    input logic [31:0] pc_next,
    output logic [31:0] pc
);
    always_ff @(posedge clk or posedge reset)
        if (reset) pc <= 0;
        else pc <= pc_next;
endmodule
